<Link id="l00104" /><CodeLine lineNumber="104"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  ///</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00108" /><CodeLine lineNumber="108"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// supplied it will be used instead (since all buffers will use the same</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00109" /><CodeLine lineNumber="109"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// identifier, the resulting files will be named &lt;ident&gt;.o, &lt;ident&gt;.2.o,</span></CodeLine>
